## ğŸ§  What Is Pattern Book Architecture?

PantheonOS is built on a new cognitive framework called **Pattern Book Architecture (PBA)**.

**LLMs donâ€™t execute code â€” they execute patterns.**

A Pattern Book is a structured set of:
